{"tid":1546813,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［重要］最後通牒！！907機場副本攻略","createTime":"2019-09-06T12:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T04:27:48.000Z","uid":234515,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"910f47bb5ec3624c72f8cf9f4813150f7a42ef5b","tid":1546813,"uid":234515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CEyx72S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCEyx72S.png&h=191ac1b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5xM4eHS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5xM4eHS.png&h=58f32d78&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FGgjN2S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFGgjN2S.png&h=e40af72b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xS9UBWd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxS9UBWd.png&h=1de1629a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信各位手足一定會集中係831太子站的集會 <br />\n但是希望大家都能夠知道聽日係機場的重要性！！<br />\n所以大家廣傳呢個post ！！！香港人缺一不可<br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">907 機場攻略(更新版)</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1) 步兵測試方法<br />\n- 和理非，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">**普通市民/旅客身份**</span></span></strong><br />\n- <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">市民/旅客裝，唔着黑色衫，冇dresscode</span></span></strong>，唔叫口號<br />\n- *<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">*可以戴普通口罩**</span></span></strong>，唔需要其他裝備 (帶左要有心理準備隨時需要棄裝)<br />\n- 地點: 同上次一樣，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">**暢達路巴士總站**</span></span>，另一個選擇係暢航路<br />\n- 策略: 到左巴士總站唔一定要企定等，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">**緊記市民/旅客身份，可以係周圍行行企企，排下隊，落車上車**</span></span></strong><br />\n- 如果有部份人真係怕係機場島走唔到，搭巴士入機場然後上返車，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">**係青馬收費廣場同機場之間不停來回**</span></span></strong><br />\n- 優先搭巴士入，建議大家首先<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">**集合左係青馬收費廣場**</span></strong></span>再搭巴士入機場<br />\n- 青馬收費廣場係交通樽頸，如果所有途徑巴士都埋站會好影響交通<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關於清場/逃走路線<br />\n- <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">**無時無刻緊記自己普通市民/旅客身份**</span></span></strong>，只要有合理原因係機場範圍出現就唔需要怕警察，上次 901 普通市民/旅客都只係企係機場島其他地方等，就算今次有咩突發事情警察決定清場都唔需要好似上次咁逃走<br />\n- 有咩合理原因可以係機場範圍出現？<br />\n接機/送機，參觀機場，巴士/地鐵愛好者，即興旅行，參觀航空探知館等等，可以參考100個理由玩轉香港機場全攻略<br />\n- <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">**無論如何都唔好係 T1/2 機場客運大樓附近設路障塞路，即使有任何行動都一定要等到三點後全部人入左機場先，手足們唔好心急**</span></strong></span><br />\n- 如果有人帶頭衝入 T1，而令到路面情況好混亂所以好多人被迫入左 T1 混入其他遊客當中，大家要緊記身份，千祈唔好係入面示威或者遊蕩違反禁制令<br />\n- 萬一警察真係清場，記得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">**緊貼其他遊客，佢地去邊大家就去邊**</span>，普通市民/旅客冇犯法係唔需要逃走<br />\n- 如果警察唔容許任何人企係巴士總站，可以去附近其他戰略性位置(例如暢航路)等到有返巴士搭,試問冇任何交通工具旅客又點進出機場？<br />\n<br />\n- 以防萬一，會盡快提供機場島，東涌，青馬收費廣場同埋青衣嘅詳細地圖，當中包括戰略性位置，所有交通路線，廁所等等<br />\n- <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">**密切留意睇Telegram頻道**</span></span></strong>，當日會安排 Bot 俾前線測試員報料<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2) 車隊測試方法<br />\n- <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">**兩點經過青馬收費廣場**開往機場幫手測試</span></span></strong>，帶多張$500找續<br />\n唔需要離開機場島，隨時準備萬一有需要時接仔女放學，建議到時可以係一號停車場附近等<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">9月7號！！！揸實政府春袋，人人有責 <br />\n光復香港 時代革命🇭🇰<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">&ldquo;多你一個好q多，少你一個有時就真是少咗一個&rdquo;</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4ceecfc9cd663f3ef59d522441097968826fe4b0","tid":1546813,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:22:18.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acc139460bd689272fd92e305c7b4552ec6d9a00","tid":1546813,"uid":234515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:23:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45015b0a18c7362f360b41215a179a6497c40f33","tid":1546813,"uid":234515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:23:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01f403c2609605275a357b3926661ed6682e9b5d","tid":1546813,"uid":234515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:23:47.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"e4484060494421455817c7e56f7e2db72c0e1c1f","tid":1546813,"uid":234515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:23:57.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"02b1083b159c5573b25f8a2ed31eb45cf9967e72","tid":1546813,"uid":234515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:24:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f305b6013c1a63b742f1a7cb1788b81b7dbecd2","tid":1546813,"uid":234515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:25:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db4b769775d1fc1da27bbdf0ffca7acad3a1bcc5","tid":1546813,"uid":234515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:25:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af3ff49d2490f0e05a07e34260c0cc7ff68ed46f","tid":1546813,"uid":234515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:25:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7f73e3d2f2bb10282b04eb4fe3defe7d4eb15d0","tid":1546813,"uid":115069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:25:46.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c9535d7017bfa9e250024c3fc98a69ab201db6c1","tid":1546813,"uid":178066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:26:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d2574f6393231b109bd0260210018e2e5b39a77d","tid":1546813,"uid":234515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:27:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a750e6a7d438bab9f09a371ed4f44d5e19001774","tid":1546813,"uid":123270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:27:24.000Z","msg":"推爆佢！！！！！！！<br />\n我要影日落！"},{"pid":"d646629e891cdf062954609469155b68f60f8b31","tid":1546813,"uid":139135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:27:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee3e51bcce426d2d94cf28ed42a13dcecaed687c","tid":1546813,"uid":234515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:27:57.000Z","msg":"推行動post"},{"pid":"defaf87d342656fee4d4ca32d33c2262c57ece41","tid":1546813,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40df566b542a50fbad452e6578fc208b9c88b2c5","tid":1546813,"uid":234515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:28:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1980b873042d84ee0fd25828fb9dd4a938f79898","tid":1546813,"uid":23179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:37:44.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856759f4f05c77e920a47e83c7d1700b33d66067","tid":1546813,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:38:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e07568d17fcbce15fd750a0009e4b76ca595d4cb","tid":1546813,"uid":234515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:38:54.000Z","msg":"Push!!!"},{"pid":"f1a183e1f7634d8403fa8a23b6c3c66540ca2b27","tid":1546813,"uid":28951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:42:29.000Z","msg":"各位關注民主自由的朋友：<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群來自香港的示威者。<br />\n由六月初至今，反對[送中惡法]抗爭開始至今，已踏入第三個月。<br />\n過百萬位香港人多次以和平、理性、非暴力方式向政府表達我們的五個訴求。<br />\n更有7名義士的不惜犧牲自己，以死相諫，試圖喚醒當權者僅餘的良知。<br />\n可惜，在中國共產黨全面控制下的香港區政府堅拒回應市民的訴求，更借助香港警察的軍事力量，歪曲事實的假消息，無形的白色恐怖，意圖消滅所有示威者。<br />\n<br />\n我們在此向獨裁政權表明，如此卑劣性之手段絕對無法令香港人退縮或認輸，直至答應廣大市民的五個訴求。<br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回逃犯條例修訂<br />\n二、收回至今所有反送中抗爭之暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷所有反送中抗爭者之控罪 <br />\n四、成立獨立調查委員會，徹底追究警察濫暴<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行真正的雙普選<br />\n<br />\n香港當前面對的已經不只[送中惡法]的政治問題。<br />\n<br />\n執法：<br />\n721元朗事件，831太子事件，刻意暴力攻擊示威者，濫捕。<br />\n警權之大，前所未見，己達至軍政府統治下的戒嚴狀態。<br />\n<br />\n司法：<br />\n為達到中共維穩目標，公然遣背法律公平公正的原則。<br />\n不斷政治檢控示威者/區議員/立法會議員。<br />\n<br />\n行政：<br />\n放仼警方使用過份武力，更加直接表明支持。<br />\n散播白色恐怖，打壓一齊反對聲音。<br />\n<br />\n人道：<br />\n凌辱及暴力對待被捕人未，包括性暴力。<br />\n故意攻擊救援人員，阻止救援人員為傷者進行急救。<br />\n<br />\n中共勢力已全面入侵香港，徹底違反《中英聯合聲明》所承諾的一國兩制。<br />\n解決當前的政治問題已不能令千瘡百孔的香港重回正軌，我們必須重新建設整個政府體制，實現民選政府。<br />\n<br />\n為對抗如此醜惡的政權，香港人經歷了無數血與汗的洗禮，然而面前的高牆已非我們可以獨自打破。<br />\n所以，我們在在呼籲各支持民主自由的國家/組織/市民積極介入，以不同的方式協助香港對抗極權國家，或制裁支持極權的人士。<br />\n<br />\n包括：<br />\n凍結個別人士在國外的資產，以經濟方式懲罰<br />\n禁止個別人士及其親屬入境，以外交方式懲罪<br />\n派員協助香港人籌組新民選政府<br />\n給予政治庇護/公民身份<br />\n<br />\n不自由，毋寧死。香港人定必採取一切可行手段，使香港邁進成為民主、自由、公義的社會。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">以上參考過往的宣言</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[認真]  既然要國際支援，點解唔講出嚟？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1546622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1546622</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔知有冇用，但我覺得要向外國講出我地嘅要求同現況，有冇可能係星期日試吓？</span>"},{"pid":"55ee1c89aaef004506ab7c798ed01b1f33f04306","tid":1546813,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:42:30.000Z","msg":"推聽日行動Po"},{"pid":"e3783d6e6ddf2e124ce0de9b2e50fe54103eb97b","tid":1546813,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:43:57.000Z","msg":"冇聽日香港站攻略/討論?"},{"pid":"569a1aa7daab5d57fdf569788a5b46cad1a5808e","tid":1546813,"uid":234515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:44:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">推po! 太子站集會的同時 聽日都好重要</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5497fe8e18ee04c22a00c48cafc8ce2907401a52","tid":1546813,"uid":234515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3783d6e6ddf2e124ce0de9b2e50fe54103eb97b","tid":1546813,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:43:57.000Z","msg":"冇聽日香港站攻略/討論?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:45:43.000Z","msg":"港鐵表示，因應政府及機管局要求，機場快綫服務由明早9時開始調整，來往香港站至機場站的列車服務每10分鐘一班車，中間不停九龍站及青衣站。<br />\n<br />\n強烈譴責港鐵封站阻礙每日數以十萬計使用機場的無辜旅客<br />\n<br />\n我覺得每個人都知會封站，但是聽日的重點唔係每個人都知"},{"pid":"a6b33c14e05b40dad79989e39cfacd6b8de262a3","tid":1546813,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:48:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ce62b93e38d71c820ba8fca684e43cb3a472dcd4","tid":1546813,"uid":234515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:49:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1944058273087891919cc540679a9b9d2170da24","tid":1546813,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:50:14.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fg5HKFh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFg5HKFh.jpg&h=b79850f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr0PclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=2b5c1510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"1c5b44d4cee9ebbb6e16aa4f9417a38afc5405d6","tid":1546813,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:50:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"82dfeb5ff91f8b53797175a61ca2f4bf058873ae","tid":1546813,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislik